 mysGarageDoors - README

 Summary
 =======
 
   Description
   Interactions

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
 Description
 ===========

 Manage the two garage doors.

 From mySensors point of view, the board manages:

  - one 'main' global child

  - two children per door:
    > an 'actor' to send and receive commands
    > a 'cover' to send position of the door.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
 Interactions
 ============

 C_SET on the MAIN global child:

 - payload = '1': raz the eeprom.
 - payload = '2': run the learning program.

 C_SET on the ACTOR child of a door:

 - payload = '1': open/close the door (push the action button).

 C_REQ on the ACTOR child of a door:

 - payload = '1': sends a custom message

